      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this meticulously maintained vehicle, which exemplifies a harmonious balance of performance and aesthetic preservation. This unit has undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection to verify its mechanical integrity and roadworthiness. The interior remains refined and well-appointed, reflecting a history of conscientious ownership. For the discerning professional seeking a dependable and sophisticated automotive asset, this offering represents an exceptional value proposition in the current market.",
      "price": 34500.0,
